attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Get ready to entertain in this spacious, stunning duplex condominium in sought-after City Point. Constructed in 2011, it is one of eight units in this well-appointed building with Victorian decorative elements, from wrought iron Juliet balconies to the copper-sheathed mansard roof. This generously proportioned (2,092 SF) 3+ bedroom, 3-bath condo with 2 deeded parking spaces offers the feel of a single-family residence with a private entrance off the rear deck and parking area. The main level, with its superb open layout, including tray ceilings, custom molding, graphite hardwood floors, a gas fireplace, a sun-filled chef's kitchen equipped with top-of-the-line appliances and granite countertops with a Calcutta marble backsplash,  and a spacious primary en-suite bedroom with a walk-in closet. The lower level, with full-size windows, houses two spacious bedrooms, a family room, and a 3rd bathroom. It's a well-maintained unit with numerous updates and plenty of storage (attachment).
